Package com.ee364project

Interface HasData

All Known Implementing Classes:
Agent, Customer, Department, Person, Problem
public interface HasData
The HasData interface defines a contract for classes that represent data. Implementing classes should provide methods for obtaining information about the data, such as its type name, headers, and actual content. The interface also includes methods for parsing and shuffling data [parsing for reading from CSV and shuffle for generating new data]
